# Pods Content Structure

This directory contains individual pod data files in markdown format. Each pod will have its own detailed page.

## File Structure
```
src/content/pods/
├── fullstack-dev-pod.md
├── tech-lead-pod.md
├── frontend-design-pod.md
├── automation-ai-pod.md
├── custom-pod.md
└── README.md
```

## Markdown Frontmatter Structure
Each pod file should follow this structure:

```yaml
---
id: "fullstack"
title: "Full-Stack Dev Pod"
description: "Ideal for: MVP builds, rapid iteration, feature pipelines"
badge: "Popular"
badgeColor: "green"
icon: "/assets/features/icon-01.svg"
teamComposition:
  - "1 Frontend Developer"
  - "1 Backend Developer"
  - "1 QA Engineer"
deliverables:
  - "2-week sprints with defined feature drops"
  - "Bug resolution, feature enhancements"
  - "Integrated CI/CD if required"
engagement: "minimum 1 month"
priceINR: "₹2.2–2.5 Lakhs/month"
priceUSD: "$2,700–$3,000/month"
hero:
  title: "Full-Stack Development Pod"
  subtitle: "Complete web application development from concept to deployment"
  description: "Our Full-Stack Development Pod delivers end-to-end web applications with modern technologies and best practices."
  image: "/assets/hero/fullstack-pod.jpg"
features:
  - title: "Modern Tech Stack"
    description: "React, Node.js, TypeScript, and cloud-native architecture"
    icon: "/assets/features/icon-01.svg"
  - title: "Agile Delivery"
    description: "2-week sprints with continuous integration and deployment"
    icon: "/assets/features/icon-02.svg"
  - title: "Quality Assurance"
    description: "Comprehensive testing and code review processes"
    icon: "/assets/features/icon-03.svg"
process:
  title: "Our Development Process"
  steps:
    - number: "01"
      title: "Discovery & Planning"
      description: "Requirements gathering and technical architecture design"
    - number: "02"
      title: "Development Sprint"
      description: "Agile development with regular demos and feedback"
    - number: "03"
      title: "Testing & QA"
      description: "Comprehensive testing and quality assurance"
    - number: "04"
      title: "Deployment"
      description: "Production deployment with monitoring and support"
testimonials:
  - name: "Sarah Johnson"
    role: "Product Manager"
    content: "The Full-Stack Pod delivered our MVP in record time with exceptional quality."
    image: "/assets/testimonials/sarah.jpg"
faq:
  - question: "What technologies do you use?"
    answer: "We use modern technologies including React, Node.js, TypeScript, and cloud platforms like AWS or Azure."
